xl-medium [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-6">🟡 <strong>Needs Adjustment</strong></h1><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">These items are <em>almost</em> correct but need a small fix.</span></p><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>barrens (Geosphere, Biosphere)</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">This depends on meaning:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">If “barrens” = <em>barren terrain</em> → <strong>Geosphere</strong> only</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">If “barrens” = <em>barren shrublands / heath barrens</em> → <strong>Biosphere + Geosphere</strong></span></p></li></ul><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Right now your tag is fine <strong>if you meant the ecological barrens</strong>.</span></p><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>bitter cold (Atmosphere)</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Correct, but note:
