an></p></li></ul><div class="relative pb-6 w-full after:border-b after:border-stroke-300 after:w-full after:absolute after:mt-3"></div><h2 class="text-xl-medium [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5 pb-1">Notes on Standardization Decisions</h2><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>Pluralization</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">All countable landforms, organisms, and features → plural.
Examples:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap"><em>guyots, gullies, gypsum dunes, heat domes, high peaks</em></span></p></li></ul><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>Hyphenation</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Hyphenate compound adjectives modifying nouns:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap"><em>groundwater‑fed wetlands</em></span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap"><em>heat‑loving bacteria</em></span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap"><em>high‑albedo surfaces</em></span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap"><em>high‑relief landforms</em></span></p></li></ul><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>Singular Concepts</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Use singular for:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">processes (evaporation, hibernation)</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">mass nouns (groundwater, hail, debris)</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">abstract ecological metrics (high biodiversity, high biomass)</span></p></li></ul><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>Capitalization</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Only capitalize:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">proper nouns</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">category names you intentionally treat as proper (e.g., <em>Halophytes</em> → standardized to lowercase unless you want it as a category)</span></p></li></ul><div class="relative pb-6 w-full after:border-b after:border-stroke-300 after:w-full after:absolute after:mt-3"></div><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">If you want, I can now apply the same uniform naming cleanup to your <strong>entire dataset so far</strong>, or we can continue batch‑by‑batch.</span></p></div></div><div class="mt-3"><div class="flex opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 ease-in-out items-center group-focus-within/ai-message-item:opacity-100 group-hover/ai-message-item:opacity-100 group-focus-within/ai-message:opacity-100 group-hover/ai-message:opacity-100" data-copy="false" data-testid="message-item-reactions"><button aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" type="button" class="relative flex items-center text-foreground-800 fill-foreground-800 active:text-foreground-600 active:fill-foreground-600 dark:active:text-foreground-650 dark:active:fill-foreground-650 bg-transparent safe-hover:bg-black/5 active:bg-black/3 dark:safe-hover:bg-white/8 dark:active:bg-white/5 text-sm justify-center size-9 rounded-xl after:rounded-xl after:absolute after:inset-0 after:pointer-events-none after:border after:border-transparent after:contrast-more:border-2 outline-2 outline-offset-1 focus-visible:z-[1] focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-stroke-900" data-testid="message-thumb