font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">You don’t need to repeat the rules — I’ve got them fully internalized. But here’s a quick, clean restatement so we’re aligned before continuing the sphere‑sorting:</span></p><div class="relative pb-6 w-full after:border-b after:border-stroke-300 after:w-full after:absolute after:mt-3"></div><h2 class="text-xl-medium [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5 pb-1">🌍 Sphere Classification Rules (Final + Locked‑In)</h2><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>Atmosphere</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Tag only when the feature <em>is</em>:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">air</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">weather</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">climate</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">atmospheric optics</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">atmospheric moisture</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">atmospheric circulation</span></p></li></ul><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Not when climate merely influences something.</span></p><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>Anthrosphere</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Tag only when the feature is:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">human‑made</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">human‑modified</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">human‑managed</span></p></li></ul><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>Biosphere</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Tag when the feature <em>is</em>:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">a living organism</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">a biological community</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">vegetation</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">animals</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">microbes</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">organic matter</span></p></li></ul><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>Geosphere</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Tag when the feature <em>is</em>:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">land</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">rock</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-