</p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">conceptual items with no physical sphere</span></p></li></ul><h3 class="text-lg-strong pb-1 [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5"><strong>Multi‑Tagging</strong></h3><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Use every sphere that directly defines the feature.</span></p><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Examples:</span></p><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap"><em>fog‑fed oases → Atmosphere + Hydrosphere + Biosphere</em></span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap"><em>crystal bogs → Hydrosphere + Geosphere + Biosphere</em></span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap"><em>constructed waterways → Anthrosphere + Hydrosphere + Geosphere</em></span></p></li></ul><div class="relative pb-6 w-full after:border-b after:border-stroke-300 after:w-full after:absolute after:mt-3"></div><h2 class="text-xl-medium [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5 pb-1">🌱 Naming Rules (We’ll apply these <em>after</em> sphere classification)</h2><ul class="relative list-outside marker:text-foreground-750 dark:marker:text-foreground-600 flex flex-col ms-4 px-1"><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Pluralize countable features</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Hyphenate compound adjectives</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Keep singular for mass nouns or conceptual processes</span></p></li><li class="ps-2" style="opacity: 1;"><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">Keep capitalization minimal unless proper noun</span></p></li></ul><div class="relative pb-6 w-full after:border-b after:border-stroke-300 after:w-full after:absolute after:mt-3"></div><h2 class="text-xl-medium [&amp;:not(:first-child)]:pt-3.5 pb-1">👍 Ready to continue</h2><p><span class="font-ligatures-none whitespace-pre-wrap">I’m fully synced with the rules.
